C ya monday, Logo!

::Striker::

Striker nods. "The Alliance is a group of bots, mostly traitors from other 
sides. They have even less mercy than the preds."

He looks at Omega (I'm assuming that Omega is near Striker?), "Welcome to the 
Maximals, Omega. Prowl's in charge temporarily."

Striker keeps flying toward the Cybertronian Fire, "If you'd follow me, I'm 
taking Hot Rod to our base, you're welcome to come along."
